<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vérification de compte - AUTOSHOP</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/bootstrap/bootstrap-5.3.8-dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff8f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #00A2EA;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header img {
            max-width: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        header h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #fff3e0;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #00A2EA;
        }

        main {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        main section.text {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        main section img {
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #00A2EA;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            main {
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 50px;
            }

            main section.text {
                text-align: left;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h3>Bonjour <%=Name%> !</h3>
        <p>Votre code de vérification AUTOSHOP est : <%=verificationCode%>
        </p>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="text">
            <p>
                Bienvenue sur <strong>AUTOSHOP</strong> ! Pour activer votre compte et commencer à publier vos
                offres, utilisez le code ci-dessus.
                <br><br>
                Si vous n’avez pas demandé ce code, ignorez ce message.
            </p>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <small>© <%=new Date().getFullYear()%> AUTOSHOP.</small>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>